headline: Otis Australia to Modernize and Transform Elevators in LAHC New South Wales Housing
summary: Otis (NYSE: OTIS), the world's leading elevator and escalator manufacturing, installation and service company, will modernize 20 elevators for New South Wales Land and Housing Corporation (LAHC), a government agency which owns and maintains a portfolio of 125,000 social housing properties across the state.
